      "title": "wing scale LC-MSMS ANALYSIS RAW DATA",
      "additionalAttributes": [],
      "projectDescription": "The LC-MS/MS was ferformed to study the proteins involved in the scale's formation",
      "sampleProcessingProtocol": "the wing scales were collected from the pupal day 6 and day 8 of bombyx mori and dissovled in the 8M urae/100mM DTT, the The protein concentration of the dissolved scales was determined with a BCA protein analysis kit. The Filter Aided Sample Preparation method was employed to digest the proteins\uff081\u03bcg trypsin / per 50\u03bcg protein, incubated at 37 \u00b0C for 20 hr\uff09and produce a highly concentrated sample without any insoluble material. Mass spectrometric analysis Q-Exactive was performed for separated tryptic peptides",
